116-| F TypeScript and build-output boundary issues | App TS configs or scripts bypass workspace package build/public export boundaries. | F-01..F-04 |
117-| G completion status and blocker drift | Planning status, open tasks, and blockers can be misread as final architecture completion. | G-01..G-03 |
